Human
+1 Con +1 Int +1 Free choice
Humans reach adulthod in their late teens and typically live less than a century, , though they can live up to 200 years with the oldest amoung them always being the wisest.
Size – 5ft to 6ft, medium
speed – 30ft
language – common +1
darkvision – 120
cyborg – natural armor 13
adv vs poison, resistance to poison.
Everlasting Energy – you are immune to exhaustion but can die from 6 levels.
Shielded mind – you re shielded against any divination magic that would be used to scry upon it or its location.
Draining Grasp – You have sensors that drain your enemies vitality. You can use the sensor as a weapon when you are grappling - Unarmed strikes 1d6 + con mod necrotic. And you gain temp hit points equal to the damage.



